  "texts": [
    "Self-MM has achieved leading results on the MOSI and MOSEI datasets, demonstrating the efficacy of self-supervised learning in multimodal tasks.Modality-Adaptive Gate BERT (MAG-BERT) [28]: Integrating a modality-adaptive gate into the BERT model, MAG-BERT optimizes the Multi-Modal Emotion Recognition Using Tensor Decomposition Fusion and Self-Supe fusion process among different modalities.",
    "It adjusts the fused modality representation based on modality-specific information, effectively learning crossmodal interactions while preserving the unique characteristics of each modality.",
    "MAG-BERT has shown superior performance across various multimodal tasks.",
    "Experimental SetupFor experiments on the MOSI dataset, a batch size of 64 was employed, with Adam as the optimizer, and the L1 Loss function was utilized.",
    "The learning rates were set at 5e-5 for text, 1e-3 for audio, and 1e-4 for video modalities."
